'Yan Majalisar Wales Ba Sa Son Zuwa Mappe'
Wasu 'yan majalisar sun nuna rashin jin daɗinsu game da shawarar da za a yi amfani da taƙaitaccen sunan MWP (daga Turanci Member of the Welsh Parliament  memba na Majalisar Wales).
Wannan matsala ta shafi shirin canja sunan Majalisar zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisar daga jam'iyyun siyasa daban-daban suna damuwa da yiwuwar yin ba'a da wannan taƙaitaccen bayanin.
Wani daga cikin 'yan kungiyar Labour, yana bayyana ra'ayin jam'iyyarsa, ya nuna damuwa game da cewa sabon taƙaitaccen rubutun rifum Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu, ba na Wales ba ne: a yaren Welsh, twp yana nufin tupice, kuma pwp  kacka.
Wani memba na jam'iyyar Wales ya ce ƙungiyarsa ta yi rashin jin daɗi kuma ta ba da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka.
Masu wakiltar jam'iyyar ta Conservative Party ba su yi jayayya da sabon rubutun ba, amma sun lura cewa MWP yana kusa da kalmar Muppet (mappet).
A wannan yanayin, a yaren Wales, ana furta haruffa w kamar yadda ake furta haruffa u a yaren Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar, wanda ke aiki a yanzu a kan dokar canja suna, ya yi wannan bayani: Sanarwar ƙarshe game da yadda za a kira Mambobin Majalisar, ba shakka, za ta kasance a gare su.
Dokar gudanar da Wales ta shekara ta 2017 ta ba da izinin Majalisar Dokokin Wales ta canja sunanta.
A watan Yuni, Kwamitin ya wallafa sakamakon binciken da aka yi game da zaɓuɓɓukan da aka gabatar, wanda ya nuna cewa 'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales' maimakon 'yan majalisa' sun sami goyon baya sosai a cikin mazauna yankin.
Game da sunayen 'yan majalisar, Kwamitin ya nuna fifiko ga 'Yan Majalisar Wales' (Welsh Parliament Members, ko WMP), yayin da MWP ya sami goyon baya mafi girma daga jama'a.
A bayyane yake cewa 'yan majalisar sun ba da wasu zaɓuɓɓuka, amma 'yar majalisa, Elaine Jones, za ta yi wuya a samu wata mafita mai gamsarwa ga kowa.
Dokokin gyare-gyare za su haɗa da wasu gyare-gyare ga tsarin aiki na Majalisar, gami da sababbin dokoki game da hana mambobin Majalisar aiki da tsarin Kwamitin.
