Gwamnatin Girka ta daɗe tana nace cewa sunan Jamhuriyar Macedonia yana nufin da'awar ƙasa ga lardin Girka, kuma ta yi ta nuna rashin amincewa da shigar da makwabciyarta ta arewa zuwa Tarayyar Turai da NATO.
Shugaban Macedonia, George Ivanov, wanda ya yi adawa da zaben raba gardama na sauya sunan, ya ce ba zai amince da sakamakon ba.
