Gidan Erdogan a lokacin ziyarar da ya kai Köln
A ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, lokacin da shugabannin Turkiyya da na Jamus suka hadu don cin abinci na safe, yanayi ya yi kyau, kuma manyan shugabannin biyu suna cikin yanayi mai kyau.
Wannan ne ranar ƙarshe da shugaban Erdogan ya ziyarci Jamus don daidaita dangantaka tsakanin kasashen biyu na NATO  ziyarar, kuma ta kasance tare da wasu rikice-rikice.
Shugabannin ƙasashe sun kasa samun fahimtar abubuwa kamar 'yancin ɗan adam,' yancin manema labarai, da kuma shiga Tarayyar Turai.
Bayan haka, Erdogan ya tafi Cologne don halartar bikin buɗe sabon babban masallaci.
A Köln ne mafi yawan mutanen Turkiyya ke zaune a wajen Turkiyya.
Don dalilai na tsaro, 'yan sanda sun hana mutane dubu 25 shiga masallacin, amma mutane da yawa daga cikin magoya bayan Erdogan sun sauka a kusa don ganin shugaban kasar.
A wannan wurin ne maƙiyan gwamnatin Erdogan suka taru, ciki har da Kurdawa, don su yi tir da muryarsu don ƙin yarda da siyasar Erdogan da kuma shawarar gwamnatin Jamus ta gayyace shi zuwa Jamus.
Akwai ra'ayoyi da suka saba wa juna a taron da ke nuna cewa wannan mutum ba shi da ma'ana: yawancin 'yan Jamus da ke da asalin Turkiyya suna ɗaukaka Erdogan, yayin da wasu ke ɗaukan shi mai zalunci.
