Amurka ta bukaci ninka kudaden da ake kashewa wajen bunkasa fasahar kere kere
Ba za a iya raina China da kokarin da take yi a fannin fasaha ba  Amurka ta kamata ta ninka zuba jari a ci gabanta na kimiyya, in ji Li Kaifu, mai saka jari da kuma dan kasuwa a fannin fasaha na AI wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wasu ma'aikatun Amurka sun yi sanarwa game da aikin AI a baya, duk da cewa a gaba ɗaya Amurka ba ta da cikakken dabarun ci gaban AI.
A daidai wannan lokacin, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta a shekarar da ta gabata: burinta ne ta zama na farko a fannin kera fasahar kere kere ta AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Ƙara yawan kuɗin bincike a fannin AI sau biyu zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, tun da yake sauran ƙasashe suna da nisa a baya na Amurka, kuma muna sa ran samun ci gaba a fannin AI", in ji Lee.
Idan aka kara yawan kudaden da ake bayarwa, hakan zai iya sa a samu damar samun ci gaba a Amurka, in ji Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa na 'Superpowers of Artificial Intelligence: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order' wanda aka buga a wannan watan ta hanyar kamfanin Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne babban darektan Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face ++.
A shekarun 1980s a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin ilimin kere kere wanda ya fi na mafi girma a cikin Otello na Amurka, sannan ya zama shugaban Microsoft Research da shugaban reshen Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya ambaci gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata, kamar ta Robotics Challenge na kamfanin Defense Advanced Research Projects, kuma ya yi tambaya a yaushe za a gudanar da gasar ta gaba don taimakawa wajen gano mutane masu tunani na gargajiya.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amirka suna yawan aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati.
Ba China ce ke cinye shugabannin ilimi ba, amma kamfanoni ne, Lee ya ce.
Facebook da Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da hasken wuta daga jami'o'i a cikin 'yan shekarun nan don yin aiki a kan ilimin kere kere.
Lee ya yi imanin cewa sauye-sauyen da ake yi a kan manufofin baƙi za su iya taimaka wa Amurka wajen bunkasa ilimin kere-kere.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da takardar shaidar Green Card ta atomatik ga masu neman aikin fasaha", in ji shi.
A watan Yuli na shekarar 2017, Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kasar Sin ta wallafa shirin bunkasa ilimin kere kere na zamani.
Li ya ce, Asusun kimiyya na kasar Sin yana ba da kuɗi ga masana kimiyya kamar yadda Asusun kimiyya na kasar Sin da sauran hukumomi ke ba da kuɗi ga masu bincike na Amirka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya a kasar Sin ya fi ƙasa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Hadakar Ilimin Artificial, wadda masana'antu da masana kimiyya za su shiga, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Musamman kan Ilimin Artificial.
A wannan watan, DARPA ta sanar da cewa za ta saka dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri mai suna AI Next.
A halin yanzu, NSF tana zuba jari sama da dala miliyan 100 a shekara a binciken AI.
Amma, dokokin Amurka da suka yi niyyar kafa Hukumar Tsaro ta Kasa a kan Ilimin Artificial ba su yi wani abu ba a cikin watanni da yawa.
