Gasar zaben Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara taron da ake yi a yammacin yammacin birnin Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne karo na farko da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya haɗa da ziyarar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tun da aka dage zaben da ya gabatar domin zama babban alkali, Trump yana neman samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na iya rasa iko a kan majalisa idan aka yi zabe a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da dare, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon taron a kan layi?
Za a yi ganawa da Trump a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin rana, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump da masu jefa kuri'a a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar YouTube.
Ana iya ganin Trump zai yi jawabi a wani sauraron da zai gudana a wannan makon game da takararsa Brett Kavanaugh a matsayin babban Alkali. Wannan takarar Trump ta haifar da mummunan martani saboda an zargi Kavanaugh da cin zarafin jima'i, kuma za a jinkirta zaben da aka shirya a majalisar dattawa har zuwa mako guda kafin FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan yaƙin shine  taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke neman zaben a watan Nuwamba su kara karuwar gudu a gaban zaben.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump na nufin cewa wadannan tarurruka guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa za su taimaka wajen "sake aikin masu sa kai da masu goyon baya", yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin kare da fadada rinjayen su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Dattijai, in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisa yana da muhimmanci sosai ga tsarinsa, shugaban ya kamata ya ziyarci jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu, saboda muna shiga cikin mawuyacin lokacin da ake tayar da hankali a kan zaben", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya ƙi bayyana sunan sa, in ji Reuters.
Wannan taron da aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling a yau zai iya jawo hankalin magoya bayan daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
Ziyarar Trump zuwa West Virginia a wannan Asabar ita ce ziyararsa ta biyu a wannan jihar a cikin wata guda, domin a nan ne ya samu riba fiye da kashi 40 cikin dari a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana ƙoƙarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattawa na West Virginia Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya ragu a sakamakon binciken.
"Gaskiyar cewa dole ne shugaban kasa ya zo domin Morrissey ya ci gaba da kasancewa a gaban masu fafatawa a cikin binciken, alama ce mara kyau ga Morrissey", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia (wanda Reuters ta nakalto).
