A ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6
Turai za ta samu ci gaba a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder bayan kammala wasan Asabar da kwallaye hudu da hudu da ci gaba 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Duo mai ban sha'awa Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci gwagwarmaya tare da nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods mai gwagwarmaya don kawo lissafin a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Björn, da ke neman ta dawo da kyautar da ta yi a Haseltin shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta rinjayi kuskuren da ta yi wa tawagar Amurka a wasannin safiya da ƙwallon ƙafa hudu, ta ci nasara 3-1.
Amurka ta fi ƙarfin juriya a cikin hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya rage rata a lissafin ba.
Ƙungiyar Jim Ferrick na bukatar maki takwas daga wasannin ranar Lahadi 12 don ta ci gaba da cin kofin.
