Woods, wanda ya buga wasanni biyu na Asabar, ya nuna haskakawa na lokaci-lokaci, amma yanzu ya rasa wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 a hudu, kuma hudu  bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta kafin wasan safiya na hudu, ya koma wurin abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu, ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Keppka da 2/1, suna matsayi na farko da na uku a duniya.
