'Yan wasan Rangers sun tsira da wata mummunan haduwa ta waje, saboda gol na Dolly Meng ya sa kungiyar da ba a tara ba ta Steven Gerrard ta ci nasara da 1:0 a Livingston.
Aiki na farko da kungiyar Aybroks ta yi fatan samun nasara a kan hanya bayan nasarar da ta samu 4:1 a watan Fabrairu a St. Johnston, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta doke Gerard na biyu daga wasanni 18 a matsayin manajan, ta bar tawagarsa ta baya da maki takwas, ta ba da nasara mai sauƙi ga Harts, shugabannin Premier na Scotland.
