Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
A cewar jami'ai, akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da tsunami da suka afku a garin Palau na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Saboda rashin isar da sakonni, 'yan tsaron sun kasa samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala, da ke arewacin Pala, wanda ke kusa da girgizar ƙasa mai karfin maki 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palau sakamakon bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palau da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palau  babban birnin lardin Tsakiya Sulawesi, wanda ke kusa da bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutanen da aka kiyasta 379,800 (bayanai na 2017).
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami.
Donggala  shi ne gundumar da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 mil) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, gundumar, mafi ƙanƙanta yanki na lardin, tana da mutane 299,200.
Kasuwancin kifi da kuma noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiya na Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Harkokin karfe na nickel ma suna da mahimmanci ga tattalin arzikin lardin, amma galibi suna da yawa a Moravia, a gefen bakin tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya halaka birnin Pala da kuma Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996 ne aka yi tsunami a yammacin yankin Donggal, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Volcanic Ring of Fire kuma tana fama da girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a shekarun baya-bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin tekun lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami, wanda ya afku a ƙasashe 14, wanda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a yammacin bakin teku na Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 6.8 ta afku a kuducin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami a gabar kudu, wanda ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 ta faru a garin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mantawai kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsayi har zuwa mita 10, wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Wani mummunan girgizar ƙasa ya afku a gundumar Pidi-Jaya a Aceh, yana haifar da lalacewa da firgici, saboda mutane sun tuna da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afku a tsibirin Lombok na yawon buɗe ido na Indonesia, wanda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma dubban masu yawon buɗe ido sun kasance a ƙarƙashin rushewar na ɗan lokaci.
